Program: Outlook
Title: Exploitation of Migrant Farm Workers in Italy
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbslk
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
The exploitation and abuse of foreign workers in the farming industry in southern Italy. Also, listeners' memorable journeys. Ashraf Ghani on his candidacy for UN Secretary General. The former homeless man on his job as a shark spotter in South Africa. Presenter: Frederick Dove.